	(62,1,'2013-05-07 16:49:56','2013-05-07 16:49:56','Privacy is dead.','Privacy Policy','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-3','','','2013-05-07 16:49:56','2013-05-07 16:49:56','',14,'http://dev.skilf.com/14-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),
	(2,1,'2013-05-01 21:42:03','2013-05-01 21:42:03','<h1><b>Watch – Know – Learn.  Free educational videos that answer life\'s most practical questions.</b></h1>\r\n<strong>SKILF</strong> is currently developing one new Life Skill video per month.   Each video is between 6-8 minutes long and seeks to explain the subject matter in a simple and easy-to-understand way.\r\n\r\nBelow please find the first video about <i>Paycheck Deductions</i>, which tackles a subject that everyone questions at one point in their life.  Do you have an idea for a Life Lesson you think we should cover?  If so, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://dev.skilf.com/contact-us/\">please contact us to suggest a topic</a>.\r\n<h3>What is all this stuff that gets taken out of my paycheck?</h3>\r\nhttps://vimeo.com/70962994\r\n<em>Video made possible by a generous donation from <a href=\"http://dev.skilf.com/assets/sites/2/BlueLogo46k1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-121\" alt=\"BlueLogo46k[1]\" src=\"http://dev.skilf.com/assets/sites/2/BlueLogo46k1.jpg\" width=\"80\" style=\"width:80px;\" /></a></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Following is a list of Subject Areas that are currently being reviewed for development:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What is a mortgage?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you open a bank account?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you balance your checkbook?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a stock?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a bond?</li>\r\n	<li>What is interest?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you buy a car?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you file a lawsuit?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you create a household budget?</li>\r\n	<li>Taxes\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What is income tax?</li>\r\n	<li>What is sales tax?</li>\r\n	<li>What are payroll taxes?</li>\r\n	<li>What is estate tax?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>What is social security?</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What is health insurance, and how does it work?</li>\r\n	<li>Car Insurance?</li>\r\n	<li>Property insurance?</li>\r\n	<li>Umbrella insurance?</li>\r\n	<li>Disability insurance?</li>\r\n	<li>Life Insurance?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Paying for repairs - what is hourly vs. contract work?</li>\r\n	<li>What is an estimate?</li>\r\n	<li>Cars\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What is MPG?</li>\r\n	<li>How do car repairs work?</li>\r\n	<li>What is the difference between buying and leasing?</li>\r\n	<li>Why do you register a vehicle?</li>\r\n	<li>What is residual value?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>What is paid advertising and how does it work?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you start a company?</li>\r\n	<li>What are the different types of companies? (LLC, Inc., etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>What is a filing system for bills and how do you set one up?</li>\r\n	<li>What is online banking and what are the benefits?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a will?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a trust?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a Power of Attorney?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a living will?</li>\r\n</ul>','Life Skills','','publish','open','open','','life-skills','','','2013-07-29 20:12:18','2013-07-29 20:12:18','',0,'http://skilf.jakedevelopment.com/?page_id=2',3,'page','',0),
	(11,2,'2013-05-07 15:24:02','2013-05-07 15:24:02','<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n<strong>SKILF</strong> is a non-profit organization founded by <a title=\"Neal Lieberman\" href=\"http://dev.skilf.com/about-us/neal-lieberman/\">Neal Lieberman</a> in 2013.  While the idea behind <strong>SKILF</strong> first burrowed its way into Neal’s brain almost 20 years earlier, it was during more recent “teaching moments” with his 3 kids, his nanny, and his co-workers that Neal realized that it was time to create a more formal environment for sharing this kind of knowledge.\r\n\r\nWhether viewed at school, at home, at work, or on the go, hopefully <strong>SKILF</strong> will help folks understand how the world works in a simple entertaining way.  For more information, please <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://dev.skilf.com/contact-us/\">contact us</a>.','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2013-08-13 20:42:18','2013-08-13 20:42:18','',0,'http://dev.skilf.com/?page_id=11',2,'page','',0),
	(12,2,'2013-05-07 15:24:51','2013-05-07 15:24:51','<h1>Sponsorship offers an opportunity to build customer relationships while helping to advance our work.</h1>\r\n<strong>SKILF</strong> is a non-profit organization whose goal is to provide life lessons to as many people as possible.  <strong>SKILF</strong> is actively seeking sponsors for each Life Skill segment to fund marketing and development.  Each sponsor will receive a spot at the beginning of each video, as well as have their logo on the Sponsor page.  If you are interested in becoming a sponsor, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://dev.skilf.com/contact-us/\">please contact us</a><i>.</i>','Become a Sponsor','','publish','open','open','','become-a-sponsor','','','2013-07-29 21:17:46','2013-07-29 21:17:46','',0,'http://dev.skilf.com/?page_id=12',4,'page','',0),
