	(72,1,'2014-03-05 17:15:57','2014-03-05 17:15:57','<h1><b>Free Educational Videos\nfor Real World Training.</b></h1>\nThere are many basic subjects of everyday life that are not taught at schools.  Sometimes these subjects are explained by parents to their children, but the parents don’t always do a good job of explaining them or don’t fully understand them themselves.  Therefore many folks don’t learn these lessons until later in life, or never learn them at all.\n\n<b>SKILF</b> envisions to change that dynamic<b>.  SKILF</b> has created short video segments that teach each subject with extensive use of graphics and real life examples.  The segments are grouped by subject area and tackle issues that everyone should understand as they head out into the world.  In some cases, these Skills for Life can act as a refresher for folks who want to review a particular subject area.','Home','','inherit','open','open','','5-autosave','','','2014-03-05 17:15:57','2014-03-05 17:15:57','',5,'http://dev.skilf.com/5-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),
