	(102,1,'2013-07-26 16:16:33','2013-07-26 16:16:33','<strong>SKILF</strong> is currently developing one new Life Skill video per month.   Each video is between 6-8 minutes long and seeks to explain the subject matter in a simple and easy-to-understand way. Below please find the first video, which tackles a subject that everyone asks at one point in their life, \"What is all this stuff that gets taken out of my paycheck?\"\r\n<h3>What is all this stuff that gets taken out of my paycheck?</h3>\r\nhttps://vimeo.com/70962994\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDo you have an idea for Life Skills we should cover? <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://dev.skilf.com/contact-us/\">Please Suggest a Topic</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Following is a list of Subject Areas that are currently being reviewed for development:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What is a mortgage?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you open a bank account?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you balance your checkbook?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a stock?</li>\r\n	<li>What is a bond?</li>\r\n	<li>What is interest?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you buy a car?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you file a lawsuit?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you create a household budget?</li>\r\n	<li>Taxes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What gets taken out of my paycheck?</li>\r\n	<li>Income Tax</li>\r\n	<li>Sales Tax</li>\r\n	<li>Payroll Tax</li>\r\n	<li>Estate Tax</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>What is social security?</li>\r\n	<li>What is insurance?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Health Insurance (Drs bill max, take what ins. Company gives them, you pay copay, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Car Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Property Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Umbrella Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Disabililty Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Life Insurance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Paying Hourly vs. Contract for repairs</li>\r\n	<li>What is an Estimate?</li>\r\n	<li>Cars\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>MPG</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Repairs</li>\r\n	<li>Car Payments/Leasing</li>\r\n	<li>Registration</li>\r\n	<li>Residual Value</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Advertising (Get you to buy stuff.)</li>\r\n	<li>How do you start a company?</li>\r\n	<li>Types of companies:  LLC, Inc. etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Filing System (where do you put your bills when they come in? how do you file or know what you paid?)</li>\r\n	<li>Online banking--cash flow benefit</li>\r\n	<li>What is a will? Trust? Power of Attorney? Living will?</li>\r\n</ul>','Life Skills','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-19','','','2013-07-26 16:16:33','2013-07-26 16:16:33','',2,'http://dev.skilf.com/2-revision-19/',0,'revision','',0),
