	(2,1,'2013-06-18 17:13:24','2013-06-18 17:13:24','This page contains all of the style options that users can create through the default Wordpress editor.  This paragraph represents normal paragraph text.  Here is what <a href=\"#\">a link will</a> look like in the text.\r\n<pre>This is the Wordpress \"Preformatted\" text, primarily used for showing code examples.</pre>\r\n<blockquote>This is a blockquote.</blockquote>\r\n<h1>Heading 1</h1>\r\n<h2>Heading 2</h2>\r\n<h3>Heading 3</h3>\r\n<h4>Heading 4</h4>\r\n<h5>Heading 5</h5>\r\n<h6>Heading 6</h6>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 14px;\">This is</span></li>\r\n	<li>an Ordered</li>\r\n	<li>List</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 14px;\">This is</span></li>\r\n	<li>an Unordered</li>\r\n	<li>List</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Bold Text</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Italic Text</em>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Underlined Text</span>\r\n\r\n<del>Strikethrough Text</del>','Style Data','','publish','open','open','','style-data','','','2013-06-27 16:07:23','2013-06-27 16:07:23','',0,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),
	(4,1,'2013-06-18 17:19:56','2013-06-18 17:19:56','<h1>Why <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-128\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7px; height: 28px;\" alt=\"vdev_logo_sm\" src=\"http://dev.vdevcorp.com/assets/sites/4/vdev_logo_sm.png\" />?\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 26px; font-family: \'FrutigerLTW01-55Roman\',\'Frutiger LT W01 65 Bold\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><em>experienced, proven &amp; cost effective!</em></span></h1>\r\nVDev, a veteran owned small business, specializes in data management &amp; technology services for both the US public sector and private businesses.  For over 10 years, VDev has provided IT, Operations and Maintenance support for large volumes of data on a daily basis, providing superior experience in off line and on line data management. Furthermore, we provide \"back office\" support to assist organizations in creating a more efficient work environment, enabling timely execution on numerous company’s specific mission and business objectives.','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2013-09-04 21:18:10','2013-09-04 21:18:10','',0,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/home/',-1,'page','',0),
	(67,1,'2013-09-04 21:13:54','2013-09-04 21:13:54','Founded in 1997, Virtual Development Corporation (VDev) is a veteran owned small business. We began with a vision of building a reliable, experienced, customer focused, professional services company. Since our inception, that vision has not changed. VDev has a veteran team of technical experts who remain loyal to our company and customers. Our employee attrition rate is exceptionally low, providing customers with dedicated employees with unparalleled passion and expertise for VDev’s work.\n\nVDev is a customer driven professional services company. We realize that when an organization excels at accessing mission critical data and managing the flow &amp; retrieval of information, they are more effective in executing their specific mission and business objectives. We utilize a systems consulting approach when working with clients on assessing issues and determining objectives.\n\nVDev is a team of dedicated data &amp; technology specialists who have a passion for Information technology and take pride in delivering quality service – to our country and our customers!\n<h2>Leadership</h2>\n<strong>Richard C. Garner – President</strong>. Rick Garner provides executive and corporate operations expertise as well as direct support for client engagements. Rick has worked in systems development, data services, maintenance and operations for over 20 years. These efforts have encompassed large-scale development projects, business process outsourcing and large-scale data management.\n\n<strong>Monica Laquatra</strong>. Ms. Laquatra is the company Business Manager in Charge, with responsibility for all aspects of business administration. In addition Ms. Laquatra is the corporate Secretary/Treasurer.','About','','inherit','open','open','','13-autosave','','','2013-09-04 21:13:54','2013-09-04 21:13:54','',13,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/13-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),
	(96,1,'2013-07-19 16:10:26','2013-07-19 16:10:26','Founded in 1997, Virtual Development Corporation (VDev) is a veteran owned small business that started with a vision of building a reliable, experienced customer focused, professional services company. By creating a stable, family &amp; friendly focused corporate environment – we have been able to build such a veteran team of technical experts. We treat our employees with respect and loyalty – just as we do our customers. VDev’s staff is the lifeline to the company’s success. Our attrition rate is extremely low- this creates a loyal and dedicated experience that we pass on to our customers.\r\n\r\nVDev is a customer driven professional services company. We realize that when an organization or business excels at accessing mission critical data; at managing the flow and retrieval of information; and at creating a collaborative working environment, they are more effective in executing their specific mission and business objectives. We utilize a systems consulting approach when working with clients on assessing issues and determining objectives. By understanding the customer environment, we are able to more efficiently and effectively solve their problems and help with attaining their goals. Additionally, by understanding their environment we are able to bring new ideas and technologies to forefront.\r\n<h2>Leadership</h2>\r\n<strong>Richard C. Garner – President</strong>. Rick Garner provides executive and corporate operations expertise as well as direct support for client engagements. Rick has worked in systems development, data services, maintenance and operations for over 20 years. These efforts have encompassed large-scale development projects, business process outsourcing and large-scale data management.\r\n\r\n<strong>William E. Wenker – Vice-President</strong>. Bill Wenker is a seasoned project manager and technical director with over 20 years of experience in the system development and information technology areas, with an emphasis on education and financial systems and operations.','About','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-8','','','2013-07-19 16:10:26','2013-07-19 16:10:26','',13,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/13-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0),
