	(43,1,'2013-06-27 19:25:24','2013-06-27 19:25:24','<h1>Employment Opportunities</h1>\r\nVDev has a culture of innovation where our employees can make a difference; we are looking for like minded, dynamic individuals to come and join our rapidly expanding team.\r\n\r\nIf you wish to submit your application, please send your cover letter and resume to Human Resources by fax, mail, or e-mail (no attachments, please). Thanks!\r\n\r\nVirtual Development Corporation\r\n206 Hilton Ave.\r\nCatonsville, MD 21228\r\nFax: (410) 744-3098\r\nE-mail us: <a href=\"mailto:info@vdevcorp.com\">info@vdevcorp.com</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nWe are currently searching for candidates for the following positions:\r\n<h3>Business Analyst</h3>\r\nMust have a minimum of 3 years experience performing business and requirements analysis. Experience developing Functional Specifications is a plus. Applicant must have a Bachelors degree or better.\r\n<h3>Test Analyst</h3>\r\nMust have a minimum of 2 years experience performing systems acceptance testing. The ability to develop test scripts, plans and procedures is required. Applicant must have a Bachelors degree or better.\r\n\r\n<em>VDev is an Equal Employment Opportunity Employer.</em>','Careers','','publish','open','open','','careers','','','2013-08-29 20:08:55','2013-08-29 20:08:55','',0,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/?page_id=43',0,'page','',0),
