	(21,1,'2013-06-27 16:12:16','2013-06-27 16:12:16','Throughout our history, we have successfully supported a range of complex systems integration, data management and application development projects for the US public sector and businesses. VDev’s consulting &amp; technical services focus on 2 main areas of expertise – data and technology services.\r\n<h2>Data Services</h2>\r\nVDev has over 10 years of experience in managing data centric projects. Our proven track record of success reveals our fluency in providing data analysis, data correlation, and management of millions of records on a daily basis. Additionally, we are experienced with the implementation &amp; management of major databases, statistical analysis projects and providing routine data extract reports.\r\n\r\nVDev has led and/or assisted numerous projects with varying degrees of responsibility, such as designing, configuring, testing and implementation of data systems. Our staff has successfully deployed many applications that encompassed multiple sub-components, including working with “configurers” to set correct data conditions/builds, test planning, case creation, execution and bug reporting.\r\n<h2>Technology Services</h2>\r\nVDev’s experienced veteran staff of technical consultants are extremely comfortable working on major systems integration projects, application development efforts, and systems support. Our team has led and assisted projects for the design, configuration and implementation of collaboration systems, business intelligence systems and data warehousing solutions.\r\n<h3><strong>Basic Services</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Application development</li>\r\n	<li>Network Support</li>\r\n	<li>Data Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Business Requirements Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Operations &amp; Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Data Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Technologies</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Microsoft – SharePoint, SQL,</li>\r\n	<li>MS Server 2000, 2003</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft Dynamics</li>\r\n	<li>Oracle</li>\r\n	<li>Unix, HP Unix and Sun Unix</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft .NET, ASP, Java</li>\r\n	<li>SAS Programming</li>\r\n</ul>','Services','','publish','open','open','','services','','','2013-09-20 20:11:10','2013-09-20 20:11:10','',0,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/?page_id=21',0,'page','',0),
	(22,1,'2013-06-27 16:31:24','2013-06-27 16:31:24','<h2>Project Experience</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Large Scale Data Management</li>\r\n	<li>Data Quality Assurance and Software Testing</li>\r\n	<li>SAS Programming (data mining and programming)</li>\r\n	<li>Oracle support and implementations</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft Networks</li>\r\n	<li>MS SharePoint Document Management &amp; Records Management</li>\r\n	<li>Complex Financial Formulas and Metrics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRecently, VDev collaborated on the large management and execution of a systems modernization project for a large government agency. This was for an “enterprise-wide” data storage and web based portal modernization effort. VDev has been working with this agency on multiple projects for over 6 years. Our team is involved in many aspects of each project from the requirements analysis to internal control and risk management processes. Our guidance and direction with the analysis and assessment of the business process management improvement plan proved to create efficiencies for the both the short and long term approval processes.\r\n<h2>Clients</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Housing and Urban Development</li>\r\n	<li>Ginnie Mae</li>\r\n	<li>Sallie Mae</li>\r\n	<li>Department of Education</li>\r\n	<li>State of Michigan</li>\r\n	<li>Lockheed Martin</li>\r\n	<li>Big Four Accounting Firms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n<o:RelyOnVML/>\r\n<o:AllowPNG/>\r\n</o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:TrackMoves/>\r\n<w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n<w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n<w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n<w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n<w:Lid