	(25,1,'2013-06-27 16:11:21','2013-06-27 16:11:21','Our company offers a broad range of technical expertise covering all phases of the information technology life cycle. When it comes to our business, we offer our customers a powerful resource and a recipe for success. Listed below is a comprehensive list of the skills and services we offer our clients. Please contact us for more information about how VDev can meet your organization\'s needs.\n<h2>Skills</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Microsoft and Unix</li>\n	<li>SAS Programming</li>\n	<li>Microsoft Networks, Security and FISMA/NIST Standards</li>\n	<li>Complex Financial Formulas and Metrics</li>\n	<li>Business Intelligence Solutions</li>\n	<li>Data Quality Assurance and Software Testing</li>\n	<li>Business and Systems Requirements Analysis</li>\n	<li>Services</li>\n	<li>IT Software Development Services</li>\n	<li>Analysis and Data Services</li>\n	<li>Data Conversion/Migration</li>\n	<li>Security Assessment Services</li>\n	<li>Security Certification and Accreditation Support</li>\n	<li>Statistical Analysis Services</li>\n	<li>Operations and Maintenance Services</li>\n</ul>\nApplication Testing Support Services (ATSS) Tool\n\nWeb-based test administration and test documentation tool\nProvides the ability for contractor and client test team members to enter and review test documentation, results and feedback on-line\nDeveloped using Microsoft SQL Server 2000\nAccessible using any web browser; Logon security provided via SSL services','Services','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision','','','2013-06-27 16:11:21','2013-06-27 16:11:21','',21,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/21-revision/',0,'revision','',0),
	(26,1,'2013-09-20 20:09:23','2013-09-20 20:09:23','Throughout our history, we have successfully supported a range of complex systems integration, data management and application development projects for the US public sector and businesses. VDev’s consulting &amp; technical services focus on 2 main areas of expertise – data and technology services.\n<h2>Data Services</h2>\nVDev has over 10 years of experience in managing data centric projects. Our proven track record of success reveals our fluency in providing data analysis, data correlation, and management of millions of records on a daily basis. Additionally, we are experienced with the implementation &amp; management of major databases, statistical analysis projects and providing routine data extract reports.\n\nVDev has led and/or assisted numerous projects with varying degrees of responsibility, such as designing, configuring, testing and implementation of data systems. Our staff has successfully deployed many applications that encompassed multiple sub-components, including working with “configurers” to set correct data conditions/builds, test planning, case creation, execution and bug reporting.\n<h2>Technology Services</h2>\nVDev’s experienced veteran staff of technical consultants are extremely comfortable working on major systems integration projects, application development efforts, and systems support. Our team has led and assisted projects for the design, configuration and implementation of collaboration systems, business intelligence systems and data warehousing solutions.\n<h3><strong>Basic Services</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>Application development</li>\n	<li>Network Support</li>\n	<li>Data Analysis</li>\n	<li>Business Requirements Analysis</li>\n	<li>Operations &amp; Maintenance</li>\n	<li>Data Management</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Technologies</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>Microsoft – SharePoint, SQL,</li>\n	<li>MS Server 2000, 2003</li>\n	<li>Microsoft Dynamics</li>\n	<li>Oracle</li>\n	<li>Unix, HP Unix and Sun Unix</li>\n	<li>Microsoft .NET, ASP, Java</li>\n	<li>SAS Programming</li>\n</ul>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','21-autosave','','','2013-09-20 20:09:23','2013-09-20 20:09:23','',21,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/21-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),
