	(81,1,'2013-07-18 19:37:24','2013-07-18 19:37:24','VDev’s consulting &amp; technical services focus on 2 main areas of expertise – data and technology services. The company has a proven and loyal professional staff committed to providing smart, efficient and superior solutions and services to public sector information technology &amp; data services problems.\r\n<h2>Data Services</h2>\r\nVDev has over 15 years of experience in managing data centric projects. We are very fluent in providing data analysis, data correlation, management of millions of records on a daily basis. Additionally, we are experienced with the O &amp; M of major data bases – managing the BI reporting, statistical analysis, data set testing…providing monthly/weekly data extract reports.\r\n\r\nVDev has assisted and led projects with various responsibilities – such as the designing, configuring, testing and implementing of multiple enterprise systems. Our staff has successfully deployed, unit tested, extensively system tested multiple sub-components, including working with configurerss to set correct data conditions/builds, test planning, case creation, execution and bug reporting.\r\n<h2>Technology Services</h2>\r\nVDev’s veteran staff of technical consultants are very comfortable working on major systems integration projects; application development efforts and systems support. Our team has assisted and led projects for the design, configuration and implementation of collaboration systems, business intelligence systems and data warehousing solutions.\r\n\r\nThe VDev team takes an active role in requirements gathering and analysis.\r\n<h3><strong>Basic Services</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Application development</li>\r\n	<li>Data Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Security Assessments</li>\r\n	<li>Network Support</li>\r\n	<li>Statistical Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>O &amp; M</li>\r\n	<li>Business Requirements Analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Technologies</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Microsoft – Sharepoint, 