	(68,1,'2013-07-09 15:10:15','2013-07-09 15:10:15','<h2>Experience</h2>\r\n\r\nVDev is based in the Washington D.C. metro area, and has provided professional services to our clients for over five years. These services have encompassed information and data technology projects both small and large, and have ranged in scope from feasibility testing to systems development and implementation. \r\n\r\n<h2>Leadership</h2>\r\n\r\nRichard C. Garner - President. Rick Garner provides executive and corporate operations expertise as well as direct support for client engagements. Rick has worked in systems development, data services, maintenance and operations for over 20 years. These efforts have encompassed large-scale development projects, business process outsourcing and large-scale data management.\r\n\r\nWilliam E. Wenker - Vice-President. Bill Wenker is a seasoned project manager and technical director with over 20 years of experience in the system development and information technology areas, with an emphasis on education and financial systems and operations.\r\n\r\nMonica Laquatra - Business manager. Monica provides operations and business management for all aspects of the company\'s administration and financial operations. She has supported the organization in this role continuously since the start up of the company. \r\n\r\n<h2>Small Business</h2>\r\n\r\nVDev is a Veteran-Owned small business.','About','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-5','','','2013-07-09 15:10:15','2013-07-09 15:10:15','',13,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/13-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),
