	(152,1,'2013-08-22 19:11:52','2013-08-22 19:11:52','Founded in 1997, Virtual Development Corporation (VDev) is a veteran owned small business. We began with a vision of building a reliable, experienced, customer focused, professional services company. Since our inception, that vision has not changed. VDev has a veteran team of technical experts who remain loyal to our company and customers. Our employee attrition rate is exceptionally low, providing customers with dedicated employees with unparalleled passion and expertise for VDev’s work.\r\n\r\nVDev is a customer driven professional services company. We realize that when an organization excels at accessing mission critical data and managing the flow &amp; retrieval of information, they are more effective in executing their specific mission and business objectives. We utilize a systems consulting approach when working with clients on assessing issues and determining objectives.\r\n\r\nVDev is a team of dedicated data &amp; technology specialists who have a passion for Information technology and take pride in delivering quality service – to our country and our customers!\r\n<h2>Leadership</h2>\r\n<strong>Richard C. Garner – President</strong>. Rick Garner provides executive and corporate operations expertise as well as direct support for client engagements. Rick has worked in systems development, data services, maintenance and operations for over 20 years. These efforts have encompassed large-scale development projects, business process outsourcing and large-scale data management.\r\n\r\n<strong>Monica Laquatra</strong>. Ms. Laquatra is the company Business Manager in Charge, with responsibility for all aspects of business administration. In addition Ms. Laquatra is the corporate Secretary/Treasurer.','About','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-10','','','2013-08-22 19:11:52','2013-08-22 19:11:52','',13,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/13-revision-10/',0,'revision','',0),
	(153,1,'2013-08-22 19:18:46','2013-08-22 19:18:46','Throughout our history, we have successfully supported a range of complex systems integration, data management and application development projects for the US public sector and businesses. VDev’s consulting &amp; technical services focus on 2 main areas of expertise – data and technology services.\r\n<h2>Data Services</h2>\r\nVDev has over 15 years of experience in managing data centric projects. Our proven track record of success reveals our fluency in providing data analysis, data correlation, and management of millions of records on a daily basis. Additionally, we are experienced with the implementation &amp; management of major databases, statistical analysis projects and providing routine data extract reports.\r\n\r\nVDev has led and/or assisted numerous projects with varying degrees of responsibility, such as designing, configuring, testing and implementation of enterprise systems. Our staff has successfully deployed, unit tested, and extensively system tested multiple sub-components, including working with “configurers” to set correct data conditions/builds, test planning, case creation, execution and bug reporting.\r\n<h2>Technology Services</h2>\r\nVDev’s experienced veteran staff of technical consultants are extremely comfortable working on major systems integration projects, application development efforts, and systems support. Our team has led and assisted projects for the design, configuration and implementation of collaboration systems, business intelligence systems and data warehousing solutions.\r\n<h3><strong>Basic Services</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Application development</li>\r\n	<li>Network Support</li>\r\n	<li>Data Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Security Assessments</li>\r\n	<li>Statistical Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Business Requirements Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Operations &amp; Maintenance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Technologies</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Microsoft – SharePoint, SQL,</li>\r\n	<li>MS Server 2000, 2003</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft Dynamics</li>\r\n	<li>Oracle</li>\r\n	<li>Unix, ASP, Java,</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft .NET</li>\r\n	<li>SAS Programming</li>\r\n</ul>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-10','','','2013-08-22 19:18:46','2013-08-22 19:18:46','',21,'http://dev.vdevcorp.com/21-revision-10/',0,'revision','',0),
