	(4,1,'2014-03-04 22:01:11','2014-03-04 22:01:11','<h2>What are you trying to accomplish?</h2>\r\n\r\nAdvance a public policy?  Sell your products or services?  Manage a crisis?  Educate the public?  Strengthen your brand?  Build investor awareness?  Motivate employees?  Or something else?\r\n\r\nCentral to all of these goals is communication.  If your audience is uninformed, misinformed or apathetic, you lose.  And in today’s complex and noisy world, communcations is more challenging than ever.  \r\n\r\nBe heard.  Have an impact.   We can help.','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2014-03-07 15:46:10','2014-03-07 15:46:10','',0,'http://dev.kenneallycompany.com/?page_id=4',-1,'page','',0),
